message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $150. Considering its high quality and the benefits it provides, I believe this is an excellent opportunity for you to enhance your experience. I kindly propose a special introductory price of $140 for you, reflecting my commitment to making this valuable resource accessible to you. I look forward to your positive response and the opportunity to serve you.
